```

**Timers not cleared**
```js
// Bad
setInterval(poll, 1000); // never stops

// Fix
const timer = setInterval(poll, 1000);
// on shutdown:
clearInterval(timer);
```

**Stream not consumed/destroyed**
```js
// Fix — always destroy on error
stream.on('error', () => stream.destroy());
```

